knowledge_entries.title: Safety Procedures for Machine Startup
knowledge_entries.description: Always perform a visual inspection before starting any machinery. Check for loose parts, proper lubrication, and ensure all safety guards are in place. Follow the lockout/tagout procedures.

knowledge_entries.title: Troubleshooting Conveyor Belt Issues
knowledge_entries.description: Common issues include belt misalignment, unusual noise, and reduced speed. Check belt tension first, then inspect rollers and bearings. Clean debris regularly to prevent buildup.
